Work Experience

Machine Learning Engineer

September 2021 - May 2022

Full-time Coop Work at Flex Artificial Intelligence

Flex Artificial Intelligence Inc. aims to develop a mobile app to make fitness simpler and easier. The machine learning team aims to use deep learning to provide feedback to users' exercise videos.

As a Machine Learning Engineer here, I designed, trained, and finetuned a multi-head image classifier and a video classifier for error detection of exercise videos using Pytorch. In addition, for demo purposes, I also developed a video pipeline to create feedback videos for exercise videos using the AWS platform.

Last but not least, I kept reading and learning about most recent and state-of-the-art designs in computer vision, such as ResNet, MoviNet, Squeeze-and-Excitation Network, etc.
